{"tid":1052741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國收緊支那留學生簽證 支那學生會聯署要求放寬限制","createTime":"2019-03-08T13:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T02:26:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"63182ae3c705f0aa70230123bd8571971044a5e1","tid":1052741,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"Chinese students caught in trade war crossfire urge United States to ease visa curbs<br />\n<br />\nOpen letter from student associations in US rallies support for petition, with one association leader citing &lsquo;groundless suspicion and slanders about Chinese students and scholars&rsquo; At least 100 Chinese students have experienced visa delays that put studies at risk, according to WeChat post...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2189168/chinese-students-caught-trade-war-crossfire-urge-united-states\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fsociety%2Farticle%2F2189168%2Fchinese-students-caught-trade-war-crossfire-urge-united-states&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=99f29048\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2189168/chinese-students-caught-trade-war-crossfire-urge-united-states</a>"},{"pid":"ca4af114b3bd9b27220a4ba70b98ba7e4dadadea","tid":1052741,"uid":48083,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"美國留學簽證拒簽率激增!中國學生赴美留學平等性何在?<br />\n<br />\n過去一年以來，中國留學生申請美國留學簽證拒簽率持續上升，已達10年來最高峰。<br />\n<br />\n隨著中美關係不斷陷入僵局，赴美的中國留學生也面臨著新的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n更讓人想不到的是，即便已經拿到簽證，返美續簽也會被拒簽。<br />\n<br />\n中國赴美留學生對簽證是否能通過真真兒是捏了一把汗!<br />\n<br />\n去年5月開始，美國正式收緊留學簽證。<br />\n<br />\n有不少學生反映說，12月申請美國簽證，或者返回美國的續簽，時至今日還沒有辦理下來。尤其是科技相關專業的博士和研究生，成了被審查的重災區。<br />\n<br />\n更甚之，有學生之前續簽時，被check了18個月，而最終也無法繼續學業!<br />\n<br />\n汗顏!<br />\n<br />\n簽證遇到困難的學生，聯繫了美國大使館，但得到的是千篇一律的答復，那就是：耐心等待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hfo4qXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfo4qXn.png&h=23c02424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對此，大家聯合各學校的中國學生會自發向美國國國務院遞交請願書，為留學生群體發聲。<br />\n<br />\n受到影響的留學生有大部分是攻讀博士學位的同學，本身的學業難度就很大，現由於簽證問題延誤學業，整日憂心忡忡，身心飽受極大傷害。對此，美國很多大學也非常不滿。之前斯坦福大學就「懟」特朗普，呼籲給予中國學生平等的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果中國留學生在機器人、航空和高科技製造業等領域學習，他們的簽證有效期將被限制在1年</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n但美國大使館方面卻對此現象予以否認。<br />\n<br />\n留學監理網小編溫馨提醒大家：形式雖然嚴峻，但准留學生們也不要驚慌，正常準備申請，拿到正規大學或是名望口碑學術嚴謹大學的offer，簽證申請通過不是無望之事!<br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家留學路上一路順風!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sohu.com/a/299625524_119033/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F299625524_119033%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=b239b4c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sohu.com/a/299625524_119033/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79bf00f1e09ae91c3ac8d7eafa5e10c7af2fa90","tid":1052741,"uid":45572,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"強國人講平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dba5bde1a20259afbe2175566aa926c11fc545","tid":1052741,"uid":121146,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"愛國點解唔讀清華北大？"},{"pid":"767510e9414cf58ac9a09e3d6eb29d3212793949","tid":1052741,"uid":42283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇直接話你間諜已經好比面"},{"pid":"5afec5b01aa36b671c3320af0f178ce71e39f0a9","tid":1052741,"uid":58552,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"就係賤種 <br />\n又要愛國 又要屌美 但去美國讀書"},{"pid":"7a1d6998ef6b